Deployment JSON files are generated here by `forge script script/Deploy.s.sol`.
The file is named {chainId}.json (e.g. 8453.json for Base mainnet).

Example output:
{
  "chainId": 8453,
  "PlatformFactory": "0x...",
  "PlatformNFTRegistry": "0x..."
}

These addresses are read by:
- backend/.env (PLATFORM_FACTORY_ADDRESS, PLATFORM_NFT_REGISTRY_ADDRESS)
- frontend/.env (if direct contract reads are needed)
